  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Prevent Sexual Abuse for 1250 children in Colombia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Child sexual abuse in Colombia is one of the worst harms that affect children. Only in 2011, 593 children were abused in Medellin. Corpolatin organizes and conducts workshops focused on prevention in public educational institutions with the participation of teachers, children and their parents to avoid this problem from happening. By receiving your support we can reach up to 1250 children, 120 parents and 50 teachers, who will be child rights ambassadors and defenders.</narrative>
  </description>
